<br>
VoF tried and failed on AoW. They did Idol unslowed and whooped his backside, so in doing that, they went for AoW and failed. The debate now is VoF may not do this again back to back, or possibly till they get their next Statue rotation, so that AoW will not be wasted. What the hell do you mean they can't try again or anyone else?<br>
<br>
